<!-- ========== 區塊 4：天災現金救助 ========== -->
<div class="subs-sections" id="subs-disaster">
  <div class="subs-sec-card">
    <div class="subs-sec-header">
      <div class="subs-sec-icon" style="background:rgba(198,40,40,.1);color:#c62828;"><i class="fas fa-cloud-showers-heavy"></i></div>
      <div><h2>天災現金救助</h2><p>遇到天然災害，政府公告後 10 個工作日內至公所申請。</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="subs-sec-body">

      <!-- 5 步驟流程 -->
      <h3 class="subs-sub-title"><i class="fas fa-route"></i> 申請流程</h3>
      <div class="subs-step-flow">
        <div class="subs-step"><div class="subs-step-num" style="background:#c62828;">1</div><div class="subs-step-content"><strong>天災發生</strong><div class="subs-step-sub">颱風、洪水、寒害、乾旱等天然災害造成農業損失</div></div></div>
        <div class="subs-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="subs-step"><div class="subs-step-num" style="background:#c62828;">2</div><div class="subs-step-content"><strong>農業部公告救助地區</strong><div class="subs-step-sub">由農業部勘查後公告適用救助的地區與作物</div></div></div>
        <div class="subs-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="subs-step"><div class="subs-step-num" style="background:#c62828;">3</div><div class="subs-step-content"><strong>10 工作日內申請</strong><div class="subs-step-sub">自公告翌日起算，攜帶文件至<strong>受災地鄉（鎮/市/區）公所</strong>申辦</div></div></div>
        <div class="subs-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="subs-step"><div class="subs-step-num" style="background:#c62828;">4</div><div class="subs-step-content"><strong>公所勘查審核</strong><div class="subs-step-sub">公所派員現場勘查損害面積與程度</div></div></div>
        <div class="subs-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="subs-step"><div class="subs-step-num" style="background:#c62828;">5</div><div class="subs-step-content"><strong>撥入帳戶</strong><div class="subs-step-sub">審核通過後救助金撥入農民帳戶</div></div></div>
      </div>

      <!-- 文件清單 -->
      <h3 class="subs-sub-title" style="margin-top:28px;"><i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i> 申請應備文件</h3>
      <div class="subs-doc-grid">
        <div class="subs-doc-card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-wheat-awn" style="color:#2e7d32;"></i> 農作物</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>身分證正本及影本</li>
            <li>土地所有權狀或登記簿謄本</li>
            <li>承租者需附有效期間內之土地租賃契約或委託經營契約</li>
            <li>農會存摺影本（撥款用）</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="subs-doc-card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-fish" style="color:#1565c0;"></i> 養殖漁業</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>養殖漁業登記證</li>
            <li>放養量申報證明</li>
            <li>水權（源）證明（陸上養殖）</li>
            <li>區劃漁業權執照或專用漁業權入漁證明（海上養殖）</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 救助額度 -->
      <h3 class="subs-sub-title" style="margin-top:28px;"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 雲嘉常見作物救助額度參考</h3>
      <div class="subs-table-wrap">
        <table class="subs-data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>作物</th><th>每公頃救助金（參考）</th><th>備註</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>水稻</td><td><strong>18,000 元</strong></td><td>台灣最大宗作物</td></tr>
            <tr><td>玉米</td><td>12,000 元</td><td>雜糧類</td></tr>
            <tr><td>落花生</td><td>30,000 元</td><td>雲嘉重要雜糧</td></tr>
            <tr><td>蔬菜類</td><td>60,000 元</td><td>短期葉菜</td></tr>
            <tr><td>果樹（柑橘、芒果等）</td><td>36,000–54,000 元</td><td>依果樹種類而異</td></tr>
            <tr><td>水產養殖</td><td>依物種及損失率</td><td>需有養殖登記證</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="subs-note-box" style="border-color:#fca5a5;background:#fef2f2;">
        <i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation" style="color:#c62828;"></i>
        <span><strong>關鍵提醒：</strong>天災救助有嚴格的 <strong>10 工作日</strong> 申請期限，逾期不受理。災後請立即至受災地公所詢問，或撥打農業部免費專線 0800-037-038。</span>
      </div>

      <div class="subs-note-box" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
        <span>天災現金救助與<a href="/economic-insurance/crop-insurance/" style="color:#1565c0;font-weight:700;">農作物保險</a>理賠可以<strong>同時領取</strong>。建議農友在申請救助的同時，也了解農作物保險以取得更完整的保障。</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

